Trezor Safe 3

Your fortress for safeguarding digital assets. Equipped with features including the Secure Element (EAL6+) and device-entry passphrase, it’s an impenetrable security pair.

Say farewell to crypto concerns. With wallet backup, you’re covered. The Single-share Backup blends top-notch security with the latest universal 20-word backup format. Easily level up to the Multi-share Backup for an even more robust wallet backup system.

And the look? A sleek, stylish, modern design perfectly complements its robust crypto armor.

The Trezor Safe 3 hardware wallet brings together crypto security and asset management in functional hardware wallet design.

Frequently asked questions

What’s the difference between Trezor Safe 3 and Trezor Model One?

The Model One focuses on a more hands-on approach to crypto security with its OLED display and intuitive button interface. Trezor Safe 3 prioritizes security with its Secure Element chip and offers easy usability with a color touchscreen and two-button input.

What are the reviews of Trezor Safe 3?

Users' opinions are in, and when it comes to security and privacy, Trezor Safe 3 is a solid hardware wallet from the industry founders. With its built-in Secure Element layer, it's your ultimate guardian in the crypto world. Supporting 1000s of coins and tokens, it's got your back no matter what you're into.

How do I transfer my funds from an online exchange (including Coinbase and Binance) to Trezor Safe 3?

It’s easy to move your crypto stash from your online exchange to your Trezor. First, connect your Trezor device, pop open Trezor Suite, and punch in your PIN. Next, pick your receive account and copy the wallet address. Now, jump over to your online exchange, pick the cryptocurrency, paste in the address, and seal the deal with a confirmation. Voilà!

Why should I use Trezor Safe 3 instead of holding crypto on an exchange?

Keeping coins online is like playing with fire. Online exchanges are big targets for hackers. They're magnets for security breaches and can spill the beans on your sensitive data. Well, the Trezor Safe 3 is like the trusted guardian angel of your crypto, placing access in an offline, Fort Knox-like sanctuary, keeping it safe and sound.

Where can I buy a Trezor Safe 3 hardware wallet?
